               <title mediaType="text/x-hl7-title+xml">
HOW SUPPLIED
</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>As a sterile ophthalmic solution in Alcon's DROP-TAINER** dispensing system consisting of a natural low density polyethylene bottle and dispensing plug and tan polypropylene closure. Tamper evidence is provided with a shrink band around the closure and neck area of the package.</paragraph>
