                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">STORAGE: </content>Store at 2° to 25°C (36° to 77°F). Protect from light.</paragraph>
                  <br/>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Relabeling and Repackaging by</content>:<br/>STAT Rx USA LLC<br/>Gainesville, GA  30501<br/>
