               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20110723"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="splSectionAnimalPharm">
               <id root="68c53719-cdb5-4018-a842-09822f254fb3"/>
               <code code="34091-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="ANIMAL PHARMACOLOGY &amp; OR TOXICOLOGY SECTION"/>
               <title mediaType="text/x-hl7-title+xml">
ANIMAL PHARMACOLOGY
</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Ciprofloxacin and related drugs have been shown to cause arthropathy in immature animals of most species tested following oral administration.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>However, a one-month topical ocular study using immature Beagle dogs did not demonstrate any articular lesions.</paragraph>
